OL,3,CMotor finance victims urged to
OL,4,Ccomplain as compensation could hit
OL,5,C#18bn
OL,7,FMillions of drivers could be owed a
OL,8,Fshare of up to #18bn after the
OL,9,FFinancial Conduct Authority (FCA)
OL,10,Fannounced it will consult on an
OL,11,Findustry-wide compensation scheme.
OL,13,FMotorists could receive a pay-out
OL,14,Fafter it emerged many motor finance
OL,15,Ffirms were not complying with rules or
OL,16,Fthe law by not providing customers
OL,17,Fwith relevant information about
OL,18,Fcommission paid by lenders to the car
OL,19,Fdealers who sold the loans, the FCA
OL,20,Fsaid.
