OL,7,FThe authority estimates that most
OL,8,Findividuals will probably receive less
OL,9,Fthan #950 in compensation.
OL,11,FThe final total cost of any
OL,12,Fcompensation scheme is estimated to be
OL,13,Fbetween #9 billion and #18 billion,
OL,14,Fthe FCA added.
OL,16,FConsumer champion Martin Lewis said in
OL,17,Fa video posted to X that millions of
OL,18,Fpeople are likely to be due a share of
OL,19,Fup to #18 billion.
