OL,7,FHe told Sky News the consultation is
OL,8,F"likely to mean 40% of people who got
OL,9,Fa car finance deal between 2007 and
OL,10,F2021 will be due some form of redress,
OL,11,Flikely to be hundreds not thousands of
OL,12,Fpounds".
OL,14,FThe consultation will be launched by
OL,15,Fearly October. If the compensation
OL,16,Fscheme goes ahead, the first payments
OL,17,Fshould be made in 2026.
OL,19,FIt comes after Friday's ruling by the
OL,20,FSupreme Court on cases in which the
OL,21,FFCA had intervened.
