OL,7,FWhile some motor finance customers
OL,8,Fwill not get compensation because in
OL,9,Fmany cases commission payments were
OL,10,Flegal, the court ruled that in certain
OL,11,Fcircumstances the failure to properly
OL,12,Fdisclose commission arrangements could
OL,13,Fbe unfair and therefore unlawful, the
OL,14,FFCA added.
OL,16,FPeople who have already complained do
OL,17,Fnot need to do anything, the FCA said.
