OL,7,FConsumers who are concerned that they
OL,8,Fwere not told about commission and
OL,9,Fthink they may have paid too much to
OL,10,Ftheir motor finance lender have been
OL,11,Furged to complain now.
OL,13,FConsumers do not need to use a claims
OL,14,Fmanagement company or law firm and
OL,15,Fdoing so could cost them around 30% of
OL,16,Fany compensation paid, it added.
