OL,7,FTo make an initial complaint, the FCA
OL,8,Fsays people should get in touch with
OL,9,Ftheir lender or broker, then the
OL,10,Fprovider should send an
OL,11,Facknowledgement within eight weeks.
OL,13,FUnder the FCA's current rules, it will
OL,14,Fnot have to send a final response
OL,15,Funtil after December 4 2025. But as
OL,16,Fthe FCA is consulting on a
OL,17,Fcompensation scheme, the deadline may
OL,18,Fbe extended.
