OL,7,FIf customers are unhappy with their
OL,8,Fprovider's response, they can then
OL,9,Fcomplain to the Financial Ombudsman
OL,10,FService, the FCA added.
OL,12,FThe authority will propose rules on
OL,13,Fhow lenders should "consistently,
OL,14,Fefficiently and fairly" decide whether
OL,15,Fsomeone is owed compensation and how
OL,16,Fmuch. It will monitor if firms are
OL,17,Ffollowing the rules and act if they
OL,18,Fare not.
