OL,7,FNikhil Rathi, chief executive of the
OL,8,FFCA, said: "It is clear that some
OL,9,Ffirms have broken the law and our
OL,10,Frules. It's fair for their customers
OL,11,Fto be compensated.
OL,13,F"We also want to ensure that the
OL,14,Fmarket, relied on by millions each
OL,15,Fyear, can continue to work well and
OL,16,Fconsumers can get a fair deal.
