OL,7,F"Our aim is a compensation scheme
OL,8,Fthat's fair and easy to participate
OL,9,Fin, so there's no need to use a claims
OL,10,Fmanagement company or law firm. If you
OL,11,Fdo, it will cost you a significant
OL,12,Fchunk of any money you get.
OL,14,F"It will take time to establish a
OL,15,Fscheme but we hope to start getting
OL,16,Fpeople any money they are owed next
OL,17,Fyear."
